data.title: Rahul Mahajan
data.meta_description: Rahul Mahajan is an Indian[citation needed] reality show entertainer and former pilot. He is the son of former union cabinet minister Pramod Mahajan. He appeared as a contestant on reality show Bigg Boss 2 and again in Bigg Boss Halla Bol
